Explore Sri Lanka’s Cultural Triangle with Browns Hotels & Resorts and experience a journey rich in heritage, adventure, and wellness.

🏛️ Hotel Sigiriya – Enjoy the epic view of Lion Rock and stay just steps away from one of the UNESCO’s most iconic landmarks.

🌿 Occidental Paradise Dambulla – Surrounded by lush greenery and ancient stories, it’s perfect for adventurers ready to hike, explore, and discover something new every day.

🧘‍♀️ Ayugiri Wellness Resort, Sigiriya – Slow things down with wellness rituals, authentic Ayurveda, and peaceful moments designed just for you.

Three unique stays. One unforgettable journey. All with the warm Sri Lankan hospitality you’ll always remember.

Browns Elev8 Youth Skill Camp 2025 | Next Gen. Next Leaders. 🌍🙌

The future of hospitality is in good hands and it just got a major boost! Organised by Browns Hotels & Resorts, the Elev8 Youth Skill Camp 2025 brought together our young hoteliers from across the Browns Hotels & Resorts and @revealthecollection family, along with invited hospitality and tourism undergraduates from @cinec_campus for a full-on day of energy, learning, and inspiration at Browns Hotels and Resorts HQ. 

Led by Eksath Wijerathne, CEO of Browns Hotels & Resorts, and Shashi Jayawardena, ex-hotelier and certified master trainer, the camp was all about shaping the mindset of tomorrow’s leaders - through team games, life skills, career talks, and a whole lot of fun!

And true to its name, Elev8 pushed everyone higher - expanding the horizons of these young mindsets in eight different skill sets and building the kind of energy only the next generation of hospitality leaders can bring.

This wasn’t just another camp. It was a launchpad for the next generation of hospitality.
